   "fontSize": 10,
   "fontFamily": 5,
   "text": "1 prepare run dir \u00b7 copy data\n2 preview data (schemas\u00b7heads)\n3 inject playbook + similar runs\n4 policy: draft | debug | improve\n5 LLM writes complete script\n6 static gate (AST pre-check)\n7 sandbox exec (fitted timeout)\n8 forced-tool review + override\n9 journal append \u00b7 crash-safe save\n10 loop until steps/time/token budget",
   "textAlign": "center",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "1 prepare run dir \u00b7 copy data\n2 preview data (schemas\u00b7heads)\n3 inject playbook + similar runs\n4 policy: draft | debug | improve\n5 LLM writes complete script\n6 static gate (AST pre-check)\n7 sandbox exec (fitted timeout)\n8 forced-tool review + override\n9 journal append \u00b7 crash-safe save\n10 loop until steps/time/token budget",
   "lineHeight": 1.3,
   "baseline": 126
